Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:54.93,Kaguya_hm_FOT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\pos(1806,476)}稍微加了點料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:55.01,Kaguya_hm_FOT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\pos(1806,476)}稍微加了點料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:55.93,Kaguya_hm_FOT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\pos(1806,476)}稍微加了點料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:56.01,Kaguya_hm_FOT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\pos(1806,476)}稍微加了點料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:56.10,Kaguya_hm_FOT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\pos(1806,476)}稍微加了點料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:03.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說您是來探望輝夜大小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:05.36,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord5\fs80\b1\pos(378,926)}關於四宮輝夜①
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶您去輝夜大小姐的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:14.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我就只是來給四宮送文件的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:17.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,早坂小姐幫我送過去就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都到了這了還害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:26.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不了不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:29.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您還是親手交給輝夜大小姐比較妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:36.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜大小姐 有客人來看您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:41.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜大小姐你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:42.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好亂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您在找什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:49.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:50.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,煙花？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,早坂也想一起放煙花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:54.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:57.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就到暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:59.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,著急的心情我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:01.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但要先治好感冒才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要放煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:07.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 有客人來看您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:17.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是會長！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會長會在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:21.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:23.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 今天開始住我們家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不會住 不會住的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,早坂小姐這到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:31.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,西格蒙德·弗洛伊德說過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:37.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的行動是根據欲望和理性決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.24,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H202228&\3c&HEDF6FD&}想睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的本能會生出很多欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.87,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H202228&\3c&HEDF6FD&}想揍他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:45.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,理性是抑制欲望的剎車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.08,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H202228&\3c&HEDF6FD&}想去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:45.25,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H202228&\3c&HEDF6FD&}想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:52.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果因為某些原因失去作為理性源頭的思考能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:55.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,人就會變成欲望驅使的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,總之就是變成白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:17:59.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:03.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,越是平時用腦多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:05.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候反應越強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:09.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然看起來是醒著的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:12.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,其實還像是在夢中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:14.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,恢復了以後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:18.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,生病時的事情全部都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和喝醉了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,又是奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:26.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我差不多要回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託您照顧輝夜大小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:30.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:31.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有一點請您注意一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:36.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這個房間差不多3個小時都絕對不會有人來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:39.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不要做奇怪的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:41.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:45.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 這個房間隔音效果完美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:47.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜大小姐也不會記得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,無論你做什麼都不會暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:56.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以絕對絕對不要做奇怪的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了不會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:10.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你帶了一些喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:11.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:13.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,煙花？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:20.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 現在的四宮說話沒有邏輯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:25.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話我有點邪念期待她讓我餵她之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不過她真的很難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:30.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著這個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可能能聽到四宮真正的想法或者弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:34.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮 你是不是因為我才感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:41.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:45.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天你是想要送我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,才在校門口等著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:55.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是又好像不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:56.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長你生氣了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:02.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是生氣啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:11.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我總是讓會長為難
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:17.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我呀 一直都…不知道該怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:20.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很多事都是第一次做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:22.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:27.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我只能用我會的方法
