Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會其他的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:35.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只能這樣去做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:36.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:37.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:44.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 不 四宮！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:54.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:55.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮就算醒了也會忘掉現在發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:59.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會有人進房間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這千載難逢的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也沒有自信控制住自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:11.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底會怎麼樣啊
