Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:52.16,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}我總是會顫抖著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:59.16,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}素直じゃない私を連れ出して！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:59.16,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}請帶走這樣不坦率的我！
